Boat Rental in

Ibiza and Formentera

Boat rental in Ibiza and Formentera. Explore the stunning coastlines, crystal-clear waters, and hidden coves of these beautiful Mediterranean islands at your own pace. Unforgettable experiences await you.

Discover

our fleet

Embark on an extraordinary journey and uncover our impressive fleet of boats. From luxurious yachts to agile speedboats, we offer a diverse selection that promises to elevate your maritime experience. Discover the perfect vessel tailored to your desires and set sail for unforgettable memories on the sparkling waters of Ibiza and Formentera.

bests services

BOATS

Explore the freedom of the sea with our diverse range of boat rentals. From leisurely cruises to thrilling water sports, embark on your nautical adventure today.

EXPERIENCES

Dive into a world of adventure and relaxation on our unforgettable boat experiences. Explore stunning coastlines, engage in water activities, and make lifelong memories on the open seas.

EXCURSIONS

Immerse yourself in the beauty of the ocean with our captivating boat tours. Discover hidden coves, swim in turquoise waters, and create unforgettable memories on your maritime journey.

WATER SPORTS

Experience the thrill of adrenaline and the refreshing splash of water with our wide range of water sports equipment. From jet skis to paddleboards, gear up for an aquatic adventure like no other.
